06ec9e35009&amp;language=en_US&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl&amp;asc_source=feed&amp;asc_campaign=feed&amp;asc_refurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.billboard.com%2Fculture%2Fproduct-recommendations%2Fcall-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-where-to-buy-online-1235463162%2F" target="_blank">《现代战争 III》</a></em> 。对于那些不想花时间重新收集或升级武器和装备的人来说，这是理想的选择。 </p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-iii-xbox.jpg?w=793" alt="Xbox Series X 版《使命召唤：现代战争 III》" class="wp-image-1235466091" width="397" height="512" srcset="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-iii-xbox.jpg 1162w, https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-iii-xbox.jpg?resize=232,300 232w" sizes="(min-width: 87.5rem) 1000px, (min-width: 78.75rem) 681px, (min-width: 48rem) 450px, (max-width: 48rem) 100vw"></figure></div><p class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   ">此外，该游戏还提供标准版和跨代版两个版本。首先是标准版，只有游戏。第二个是跨世代版本，它拥有游戏本身和五个不同的内容包，其中包括抢先体验、新地点、新任务、新角色等等——全部解锁。</p><p class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "> <em><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.amazon.com/Call-Duty-Warfare-Cross-Gen-PRE-PURCHASE/dp/B0CFTKVHQ2?th=1&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=billboard0ad-20&amp;linkId=ae87aef7f31ae69ef0bf006ec9e35009&amp;language=en_US&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl&amp;asc_source=feed&amp;asc_campaign=feed&amp;asc_refurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.billboard.com%2Fculture%2Fproduct-recommendations%2Fcall-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-where-to-buy-online-1235463162%2F" target="_blank">《使命召唤：现代战争 III》</a></em>将于 11 月 10 日发售，适用于<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.amazon.com/Call-Duty-Warfare-Cross-Gen-PRE-PURCHASE/dp/B0CFTKVHQ2?th=1&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=billboard0ad-20&amp;linkId=ae87aef7f31ae69ef0bf006ec9e35009&amp;language=en_US&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl&amp;asc_source=feed&amp;asc_campaign=feed&amp;asc_refurl=https%3A%2F%2