蕾妮·拉普 (Renee Rapp) 在由奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo) 配乐的新《贱女孩》音乐预告片中饰演雷吉娜·乔治 (Regina George) https://www.billboard.com/culture/tv-film/renee-rapp-mean-girls-trailer-olivia-rodrigo-soundtrack-1235466270/  Wed, 08 Nov 2023 17:21:35 +0000 CultureTV/FilmMusic NewsPopTV / Film https://www.billboard.com/?p=1235466270 "You could be really hot if you changed, like, everything," Rapp says in the new teaser.<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-paywall"><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>她的名字叫雷吉娜·乔治，她是一位了不起的人物。 <a  rel="noreferrer noopener"  href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/renee-rapp/"  target="_blank"  >蕾妮·拉普 (Renee Rapp)</a>在百老汇音乐<em>剧《贱女孩</em>》的官方预告片中饰演“The Plastics”的领军人物，这部即将上映的百老汇音乐剧改编自 2004 年蒂娜·菲 (Tina Fey) 的原版电影。猜猜哪位 20 岁流行公主的音乐是特色？ <a  rel="noreferrer noopener"  href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/olivia-rodrigo/"  target="_blank"  >奥利维亚·罗德里戈</a>小姐本人。 </p><div class="injected-related-story // lrv-u-margin-tb-2 lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-border-b-1 lrv-u-padding-t-050 lrv-u-padding-b-075 lrv-u-border-color-grey" ><div class="a-heading-border a-heading-border-background-color-grey a-heading-border-height-075 lrv-u-margin-b-075 lrv-u-margin-b-050@mobile-max"><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  lrv-u-color-brand-primary a-font-primary-bold-s lrv-u-text-transform-uppercase lrv-u-padding-r-1 a-article-related-module-title a-article-related-module-title--color-brand-primary">有关的</h3></div><div class="o-card lrv-u-flex"><div class="c-lazy-image  lrv-u-height-100p"><div class="a-crop-3x2 a-crop-1x1@mobile-max lrv-u-height-100p"><img class="c-lazy-image__img lrv-u-background-color-grey-lightest lrv-u-width-100p lrv-u-display-block lrv-u-height-auto" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/themes/vip/pmc-billboard-2021/assets/public/lazyload-fallback.gif" data-lazy-src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/renee-rapp-kesha-2023-billboard-1548.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" alt="蕾妮·拉普，凯莎" data-lazy-srcset="" data-lazy-sizes="" height="" width=""></div></div></div><div class="o-card__content lrv-u-flex lrv-u-flex-direction-column lrv-u-justify-content-center lrv-u-padding-lr-1 lrv-u-padding-lr-075@mobile-max"><div class="o_category "></div><div class="c_title "><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  a-font-primary-medium-m lrv-u-padding-b-050 u-letter-spacing-0028@mobile-max">在 Energetic 观看蕾妮·拉普 (Reneé Rapp) 与凯莎 (Kesha) 的二重唱“你的爱是我的药物”…… </h3></div><time class="c-timestamp  a-font-primary-medium-xxs lrv-u-color-brand-p